%pyproject_install
```

This eliminates the hardcoded `python3.11` reference and uses whichever Python is available in the build environment (Python 3.13 in this case).

## Required BuildRequires

The spec file needs `python-rpm-macros` to resolve `%pyproject_wheel`, `%pyproject_install`, and related macros:

```
BuildRequires: python-rpm-macros
```
